  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "This dataset was used to predict student performance by Dien et al (2020); Li and Liu (2021)).",
    "• Three real-world datasets that are called (WorldUC, Liru, and Junyi datasets) were used to develop DL predictive models in the research by Wang et al (2020).",
    "For the WorldUC dataset, there are about 10,523 records with 10 consecutive online lessons including static features (gender, age, and expectation score) and dynamic features (engagement, liveness, the relevance of learning resources and content, sentiment, and duration time).",
    "For the Liru dataset, about 1046 student's data were taken from 18 online continuous lessons including static features (gender, grade, class, and college) and dynamic features (knowledge level and assignment score).",
    "For the Junyi dataset, there are data from about 2063 students including static features (student modeling, answer time duration, problem taken in exercises) and dynamic features (answering accuracy, user taking exercises, and user answering orders)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "This dataset was used to predict student performance by Dien et al (2020); Li and Liu (2021)).",
    "• Three real-world datasets that are called (WorldUC, Liru, and Junyi datasets) were used to develop DL predictive models in the research by Wang et al (2020)."
  ]
